SUMMARY:Saxapahaw Island Park Tour and Invasive Removal (Graham)
DESCRIPTION:Join NCWF Tri-County Conservationists Chapter for a park tour and invasive removal at Saxapahaw Island Park! First\, we will tour this 30-acre island in the middle of the Haw River\, paying special attention to the early-spring wildflowers in bloom and the extensive storm debris that resulted from last July’s near-record flooding. Then\, we will help restore habitat for wildlife by removing invasive Chinese privet from the park. Come learn and lend a hand!\n \nREGISTER HERE
URL:https://ncwf.org/event/saxapahaw-island-park-tour-and-invasive-removal-graham/
CATEGORIES:Featured
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ncwf.org/wp-content/uploads/saxapahaw.jpg
END:VEVENT
