SUMMARY:Creek Week Cleanup (Charlotte)
DESCRIPTION:NCWF Charlotte Wildlife Stewards Chapter will participate in Charlotte Mecklenburg Storm Water Services’ annual Creek Week! We will work together to remove trash and debris in and around Briar Creek at Chantilly Ecological Sanctuary. Join us in restoring habitat by removing trash that harms wildlife here and downstream. This is a family-friendly event. Habitat stewards of today and the future are all welcome! \nREGISTER HERE
URL:https://ncwf.org/event/creek-week-cleanup-charlotte/
CATEGORIES:Featured
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ncwf.org/wp-content/uploads/CreekWeekCleanupChantilly.jpg
END:VEVENT
